<a class=3D"absolute mt-20 opacity-0" id=3D"user-permissions-tab" data-id=
=3D"hab_user-permissions-tab"></a><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">The <i clas=
s=3D"italic">User permissions</i> tab contains a list of all your employees=
