=3D"special-types-of-permission-profiles" data-id=3D"special-types-of-permi=
ssion-profiles">Special types of permission profiles</h2><a class=3D"absolu=
te mt-20 opacity-0" id=3D"special-types-of-permission-profiles" data-id=3D"=
hab_special-types-of-permission-profiles"></a><br><p class=3D"font-normal "=
>On the <i class=3D"italic">Permission profiles</i> tab, there are some spe=
cial types of permission profiles.</p><br><h3 class=3D"text-3xl font-bold" =
id=3D"system-default-permission-profiles" data-id=3D"system-default-permiss=
ion-profiles">System default permission profiles</h3><br><p class=3D"font-n=
ormal ">Rippling provides a few pre-configured permission profiles for comm=
on types of roles. These are tagged as <i class=3D"italic">System default</=
i> profiles.</p><br><img class=3D"shadow-md border border-opacity-25 my-4" =
alt=3D"System default permission profiles" src=3D"https://images.ctfassets.=
net/qlrvxw8mxga3/XSPWH1aFP0Y5hDR9XriH3/26a8463a4c12c3a091428a080b22f599/Sys=
temDefaultPP.png"><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">To learn more about the acc=
ess each of these profiles provides, see these articles:</p><br><ul class=
=3D"list-disc pl-8"><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal "><a =
class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=3D"https://he=
lp.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D218616651966">Super and full admins in =
