-3xl font-bold" id=3D"thirdparty-admin-profiles" data-id=3D"thirdparty-admi=
n-profiles">Third-party admin profiles</h3><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">Yo=
u may want to give access to Rippling to someone outside of your company, s=
uch as an accountant or insurance broker. To do so, set up and assign a per=
mission profile using the&nbsp;<a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:=
cursor-pointer" href=3D"https://help.rippling.com/articles/en_US/Knowledge/=
599276218499">templates for third-party admins.</a>&nbsp;These will be tagg=
ed as <i class=3D"italic">Third-party</i> profiles.</p><br><img class=3D"sh=
adow-md border border-opacity-25 my-4" alt=3D"227350197155_Answer_6.jpg" sr=
c=3D"https://images.ctfassets.net/qlrvxw8mxga3/6Btl3ocDcdJtmJ8ypgs6ZP/a6ac5=
d5cdd56e7a19addf6d72dd4049b/227350197155_Answer_6.jpg"><br><p class=3D"font=
-normal ">Learn more in <a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-=
pointer" href=3D"https://help.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D360054485034=
">our article about managing third-party admins</a>.</p><br><h3 class=3D"te=
xt-3xl font-bold" id=3D"permissions-admin-profiles" data-id=3D"permissions-=
admin-profiles">Permissions admin profiles</h3><br><p class=3D"font-normal =
">You can give someone limited access to manage permissions related to thei=
r functional area by creating a permissions admin profile. This lets you de=
legate permissions management to leaders at your company rather than relyin=
g on one super admin to manage them. These are tagged as <i class=3D"italic=
">Permissions admin</i> profiles.</p><br><img class=3D"shadow-md border bor=
der-opacity-25 my-4" alt=3D"227350197155_Answer_7.jpg" src=3D"https://image=
s.ctfassets.net/qlrvxw8mxga3/SoIKz14iqTAncEigXq8pF/4e92a31672972ff25a429d5c=
b9fa0e79/227350197155_Answer_7.jpg"><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">Learn mor=
e in <a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=3D"ht=
tps://help.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D779690109610">our article about=
 how to set up an HR, IT, or Finance partial permissions admin</a>.</p><br>=
<a class=3D"absolute opacity-0 scroll-mt-40" id=3D"i-see-new-permission-pro=
files-that-i-didnt-create-where-did-these-come-from" data-id=3D"hat_i-see-n=
