files-that-i-didnt-create-where-did-these-come-from">I see new permission p=
rofiles that I didn't create. Where did these come from?</h2><a class=3D"ab=
solute mt-20 opacity-0" id=3D"i-see-new-permission-profiles-that-i-didnt-cr=
eate-where-did-these-come-from" data-id=3D"hab_i-see-new-permission-profile=
s-that-i-didnt-create-where-did-these-come-from"></a><br><p class=3D"font-n=
ormal ">Previously, permissions for custom objects could be configured as p=
art of standard permission profiles. This recently changed; the standard pe=
rmission profile setup flow no longer includes this step. Any existing cust=
om object permissions have been migrated into separate profiles. You'll fin=
d these in the Permissions app and in the Object Permissions app. They are =
